overview: A community of women lives in an old convent that falls apart. They never talk and strive to keep everything clean. One day, Irene realizes for the first time that there is much more beyond the routine she and her sisters keep doing over and over. Irene, following natureâ€™s signs, starts a journey of reconnection with her own impulses and body to finally find her own voice.
tagline: This is the story of a 85 year old woman finding her voice
title: Daucus Carota
